replies.author: 小张up
replies.txt_content:
[08:35:48] [Netty Epoll Server IO #3/ERROR]: [WiFiCatch] Unhandled exception number 256 occured in onPacketReceiving(PacketEvent) for WiFiCatch

wificatch不能正常工作，换插件或者删掉吧。

replies.author: antilby1337
replies.txt_content: 删除WIFIcatch，这插件加载不了，请检查兼容性和版本

replies.author: Salt_lovely
replies.txt_content:
WiFicatch只能用于1.7.10服务端，检查一下版本。


protocolib在1.7服务端上要有3.7.0版本，检查一下版本
[前置]ProtocolLib —— 广为使用的前置插件[1.7-1.15]
https://www.mcbbs.net/thread-922525-1-1.html
(出处: Minecraft(我的世界)中文论坛)

replies.author: Matrixchung
replies.txt_content: 删除“[发包拦截]WiFiCatch.jar”即可解决问题。
